# Generated by `cd web && npm run build` then copied here.
# Only the committed placeholder.html stays in version control; the real
# index.html and the assets/ tree are produced by the web build pipeline.
# Naming the stub `placeholder.html` keeps `cp -R dist/. static/` from
# clobbering it, which avoids accidentally committing a build artifact.
*
!.gitignore
!placeholder.html
